<h1>The Shibe World (status: alpha test)</h1>
<img src="/TheShibeWorld/the_shibe_world_images/cover.png"/>

<h2>What is it?</h2>
<p>The shibe world is a mmo rpg based on <a href="https://www.themanaworld.org/">The Mana World</a> that accepts dogecoin transactions in-game. The Shibe World is licensed under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html">GNU GPL license</a> so you are free to play, share, see the <a href="https://github.com/theshibeworld/tmwa">source code</a> and modify it as long as it preserves the same license. It is currently under a playable unstable alpha test. Click <a href="http://178.62.248.192/online.html">here</a> to see who is playing right now.</p>
<img width="700" src="/TheShibeWorld/the_shibe_world_images/screenshot.png"/>

<h2>How to play</h2>
<ul>
  <li>
    Download the <a href="https://www.themanaworld.org/downloads.php">manaplus client</a>.
  </li>
  <li>
    Select The Shibe World.
    <br/>
    <img width="700" src="/TheShibeWorld/the_shibe_world_images/tuto_select_server.png"/>
  </li>
  <li>
    Download the patches, register and play!
  </li>
</ul>

<h2>How to use Dogecoin in-game</h2>
<p>Each character has a wallet address and can make dogecoin transactions. Use the following commands in the chat and see the results on the debug tab:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    Shows help:
    <br/>
    <b>@doge help</b>
  </li>
  <li>
    Shows your deposit address:
    <br/>
    <b>@doge deposit</b>
  </li>
  <li>
    Shows your balance:
    <br/>
    <b>@doge balance</b>
  </li>
  <li>
    Sends dogecoins to another player:
    <br/>
    <b>@doge tip [character name] [amount]</b>
  </li>
  <li>
    Sends dogecoins to an address:
    <br/>
    <b>@doge withdraw [destination address] [amount]</b>
  </li>
</ul>

